{"tid":347611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鄰國貨] 美國陸軍下令停用中國大疆無人機","createTime":"2017-08-05T03:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T15:04:15.000Z","uid":77196,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb5c2653f20d35f72d5d0b0e528695866ea0625","tid":347611,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"美國陸軍下令所屬單位，停用由中國製造商大疆創新科技公司生產的無人機，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為相關產品有「網絡漏洞」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n路透報道，美國陸軍星期三上傳一份備忘錄，引用旗下研究實驗室及海軍在5月發表的報告，指大疆的產品存在風險及漏洞，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要求所屬單位停止使用所有大疆無人機，以及大疆零件或軟件系統，並卸載各種大疆應用程式，移除所有電池或儲存媒介，以保護軍事設備</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n備忘錄指出，大疆無人機是美國陸軍在這類現成裝備中使用最廣泛的一種。<br />\n<br />\n五角大廈一名發言人表示，陸軍已在斟酌就這項政策發布聲明。大疆公司則暫無回應。"},{"pid":"f3b0256434a1d341e59691552ae131eccf844154","tid":347611,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76267b984e5d5475f654b37e2a0479cf48bee1f5","tid":347611,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:36:04.000Z","msg":"可以喺server停到你機嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲點會用"},{"pid":"cb30624f70ba110b3d43f3a2b002eeb430b19ce6","tid":347611,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"應該會照copy一部靜音版"},{"pid":"35e83bcbdf68af7a3e0e51a432fff34f9a19700e","tid":347611,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"Yamaha整左咁多年都無人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75e8999e49233d943bcfaf6bd59a76c4466b977","tid":347611,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"備忘錄指出，大疆無人機是美國陸軍在這類現成裝備中使用最廣泛的一種。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"